\s UMUCO WO KUKAGOROBA WARATSE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Umuco wo kukagoroba waratse, inzamba y’igihe ca nyuma yaravuze, \bd*\bd Ijambo \bd*\bd ry’igihe ca nyuma ryaravuze iryo \bd*\bd Jambo \bd*\bd ryazanany’\bd*\bd  Ubushobozi \bd*\bd riza rihishura Yesu Kristo.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’Umuco waka w’Umwami n’Ijambo ritang’\bdit*\bdit  Ubugingo \bdit*\bdit iryo Jambo ni\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit Yesu Kristo yaje, \bdit*\bdit Yihishura \bdit*\bdit mu minsi ya nyuma aza ar’Umwami \bdit*\bdit atang’\bdit*\bdit  Ubugingo\bdit*\bdit , ni we Jambo w\bdit*\bdit ’\bdit*\bdit Imana.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umuco wo ku\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd kagoroba waratse, wakana \bd*\bd Ubuntu \bd*\bd bwinshi cane, abana b’Imana barawubona ivyari binyegejwe birahishurwa, uwo \bd*\bd Muco \bd*\bd n’umuco w’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd bugingo.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’Umuco waka w’Umwami n’Ijambo ritang’ Ubugingo iryo Jambo ni Yesu Kristo yaje, Yihishura mu minsi ya nyuma aza ar’Umwami atang’ Ubugingo, ni we Jambo w\bdit*\bdit ’\bdit*\bdit Imana.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umuco wo ku\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd kagoroba waratse, wakana abo mu mwiza ubahuma amaso, ntibigera bawubona namba abandi nabo bakira ubumenyi, ntibameny’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd uwo Muco ic’ari co.\bd*
