\zoli1 \bd N’ubu uwo Muco urakomeza kwaka, abana b’Imana bakomeza kuwubona, kuko uwo Muco ari Yesu Kristo arongora \bd*\bd Ishengero\bd*\bd , mu \bd*\bd Kuri \bd*\bd kwose, n’Umwami w’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd bugingo mu biwe\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit N’Umuco waka w’Umwami n’Ijambo ritang’ Ubugingo iryo Jambo ni Yesu Kristo yaje, Yihishura mu minsi ya nyuma aza ar’Umwami atang’ Ubugingo, ni we Jambo w\bdit*\bdit ’\bdit*\bdit Imana.\bdit*
